Lustre bash scripts

mds backup script:  script to run via cron to provide lustre backups, uses lvm snapshots (work in progress)

make_ost: creates an ost on an oss, using zfs as the backend

make_mdt: creates the mdt (work in progress)

zfs_mon: uses the /etc/ldev.conf file and the zpool status command to check the status on
	osts wtih a zfs back end.
